cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM 

The paper deals with image analysis and classification, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The proposed method involves learning discriminative features, which is a common task in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of dictionaries, which is a common technique in information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the three real-world image databases used in the experiments involve different types of medical images, which could fall under the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
